name: Reservas Ativas ou Novas
query:
SELECT name as "N. Reserva:data:120",numero_cliente as "Nome do Cliente:data:100", 
check_in as "Data Entrada:datetime:200",check_out as "Data Saida:datetime:100",numero_quarto as "Quarto Numero:data:100", booked_by as "Feita por:data:200",reservation_status as "Status:data:50", pay_advance as "Pago em Avanco:data:50" FROM tabReservas WHERE(reservation_status LIKE "Ativo" OR "Novo");
